    public abstract class DelegatingCamera

        public void addRefExternal()
        Description copied from interface: RefCountedCamera
        The external reference count is kept distinguished from internal RefCounted refs. When the last external ref count is released, the camera will stop streaming (releaseing more internal refs) and (likely) ultimately close.
